Fourth Department,

January, 1958 *

(January 15, 1958) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Ferdinand Baumgart, Appellant.

Not published with other decisions of Jan. 15, 1958, 5 A D 2d 800.— [Rep.

Motion granted to appeal on original papers, five typewritten briefs and George M. Donohue, Esq., of Niagara Falls assigned as attorney to conduct appeal; time for argument of appeal enlarged to include March 1968 Term of court.
